# agentic-os .gitignore
# Covers all four sub-projects: work-os, career-os, personal-os, meeting-os.
#
# NOTE: We use `Dir/*` (not `Dir/`) so that git still traverses the directory
# and honors the `!**/.gitkeep` exception below — otherwise the stubs that
# preserve the directory structure for fresh clones would be invisible.

# === User content (always private) — exclude contents, not the dir itself ===
# Work-os
**/Active/*
**/Projects/*
**/Career/*
**/Knowledge/*
**/Archive/*
**/Deliverables/*
**/Clients/*
# Personal-os
**/Tasks/*
**/Inbox/*
# Career-os
**/Applications/*
**/Resumes/*
**/Stories/*
**/Impact-Library/*
**/Learnings/*
# Meeting-os
**/Meetings/*
**/Decisions/*
**/Actions/*
**/People/*

# Keep the directory stubs visible after clone
!**/.gitkeep

# === Per-user generated files (only templates ship) ===
GOALS.md
BACKLOG.md
INBOX.md
!GOALS-template.md
!BACKLOG-template.md
!INBOX-template.md
!inbox-template.md

# === Hook-generated activity logs (must never be committed) ===
.work-os-activity.log
*-activity.log
.activity.log

# === Claude Code local config (must never be committed) ===
.claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/settings.local.json

# === Generated health reports ===
.health/

# === Secrets — defense in depth (no key should ever be in this repo) ===
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
credentials.json
service_account*.json
client_secret*.json

# === OS files ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# === Editor files ===
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# === Backup files ===
*.bak
*.backup
